^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Here is why I think there might be some confusion. If someone makes a Bergen Limit Raise (e.g 1@H-P-3@C), that is not game forcing. Any bids below 3@H (in this case obviously only 3@D) are game tries, not slam tries. Any bids above 3@H (which, by definition force the bidding to at least 4@H) are slam tries and control bids. |
